@diecui1202 many thanks, the problem resolved. Indeed, it caused by my pojo, the following code will case recursive calling on converting pojo to map as dubbo will convert every method starts with get to a map field. to correct this, we can change the method name which don't start with get 
 
e.g.

Class Person{
Person getPerson(){
return this
}

}

